<D>__{it's the good spirit of the forest.}
<C>__{felix}
<D>__{who's been filling your head?}
<C>__{grandfather}
<D>__{it does no harm.}
<C>__{felix}
<P>__{(peers at him)}
<D>__{oh, i see.}
<C>__{thomas}
<D>__{is it, papa? is it the good spirit?}
<A>__{felix and marie exchange a look. he's not as amused as she is, but lets it go. she smiles at the children.}
